00:17:50.958 --> 00:17:55.875
Just like most grains,

00:18:01.499 --> 00:18:02.499
preparing and cooking
quinoa is easy.

00:18:02.625 --> 00:18:06.042
Before distribution,

00:18:06.417 --> 00:18:07.499
commercially milled
quinoa usually undergoes

00:18:07.583 --> 00:18:10.042
a process that removes
its outer coating

00:18:10.209 --> 00:18:12.875
called saponins.

00:18:13.042 --> 00:18:14.625
Since saponins are responsible

00:18:14.791 --> 00:18:16.541
for the grain's bitter taste,

00:18:16.708 --> 00:18:18.583
most consumers still rinse
the grains in cold water

00:18:18.750 --> 00:18:21.791
before cooking just to make sure

00:18:21.958 --> 00:18:24.417
they eliminate saponin residue.

00:18:24.499 --> 00:18:26.666
Now, to cook quinoa.

00:18:28.833 --> 00:18:30.250
Just follow these
two easy steps.

00:18:30.417 --> 00:18:32.833
First, in a pot put
one part of the grain

00:18:34.791 --> 00:18:38.499
to two parts liquid
and bring it to a boil.

00:18:38.499 --> 00:18:42.125
And second, once it's boiling,

00:18:47.499 --> 00:18:49.875
reduce the heat to simmer

00:18:50.499 --> 00:18:51.708
and cover the pot

00:18:55.209 --> 00:18:56.292
until the grains
become translucent.

00:18:56.459 --> 00:18:58.541
One basic indication
that the grain is cooked

00:19:00.499 --> 00:19:03.292
is the presence of a white
germ spiraling like a tail.

00:19:03.459 --> 00:19:07.499
Cooking quinoa this way
will take about 15 minutes.

00:19:07.917 --> 00:19:11.334
When cooked, quinoa seeds
look creamy and fluffy

00:19:12.666 --> 00:19:15.625
with a crunchy
texture which makes it

00:19:17.042 --> 00:19:19.083
a very interesting dish.

00:19:19.250 --> 00:19:21.499
Quinoa seeds can also
be processed into flour.

00:19:22.833 --> 00:19:25.958
100 percent quinoa flour
is heavy in texture,

00:19:26.417 --> 00:19:29.625
so most manufacturers
mix it with other flours

00:19:29.791 --> 00:19:32.750
like tapioca flour
and rice flour.

00:19:32.917 --> 00:19:36.167
Quinoa flour is gluten-free,

00:19:36.499 --> 00:19:38.334
so it's a very good
alternative for people

00:19:38.499 --> 00:19:40.875
who might have
allergic reactions

00:19:41.042 --> 00:19:43.000
to gluten based products.

00:19:43.167 --> 00:19:45.292
Now the leaves of the quinoa
plant are also edible.

00:19:45.583 --> 00:19:48.875
Just like spinach, it
can be blanched, boiled,

00:19:49.499 --> 00:19:52.499
and even served raw as a salad.

00:19:52.499 --> 00:19:55.125
It can also produce an
extract that can be used

00:19:55.875 --> 00:19:58.499
in tonics, puddings and syrups.

00:19:58.583 --> 00:20:01.583
Here's a quick chocolate
breakfast porridge recipe

00:20:02.292 --> 00:20:04.666
using quinoa.

00:20:04.833 --> 00:20:06.250
Prepare the following:

00:20:09.499 --> 00:20:10.541
One half cup of quinoa.

00:20:12.417 --> 00:20:14.125
One cup of water.

00:20:14.625 --> 00:20:15.833
Two thirds cup of
chocolate soy milk.

00:20:17.417 --> 00:20:19.541
One tablespoon of cocoa powder.

00:20:20.375 --> 00:20:22.459
One tablespoon of maple syrup.

00:20:23.499 --> 00:20:25.750
And one banana, mashed.

00:20:26.209 --> 00:20:28.292
In a pot, put quinoa and
water and bring it to a boil.

00:20:29.499 --> 00:20:33.499
Reduce heat and then add
the chocolate soy milk.

00:20:35.708 --> 00:20:39.292
Let it simmer for
five to seven minutes.

00:20:39.459 --> 00:20:42.167
Or until most of the liquid part

00:20:44.209 --> 00:20:45.708
has been absorbed by the quinoa.

00:20:45.875 --> 00:20:48.209
Remove from heat and
then stir in the rest

00:20:49.541 --> 00:20:51.917
of the ingredients.

00:20:52.083 --> 00:20:53.500
The cocoa powder,
maple syrup and banana.

00:20:54.875 --> 00:20:58.042
You can make it more delicious

00:20:59.125 --> 00:21:00.375
by adding chopped
nuts or berries.

00:21:00.499 --> 00:21:03.167
And for a burst of flavor,

00:21:03.499 --> 00:21:04.917
put a dash of ground cinnamon

00:21:05.083 --> 00:21:06.791
or a drop of vanilla extract.

00:21:06.958 --> 00:21:09.499
Another recipe you can try
with quinoa is a salad.

00:21:09.917 --> 00:21:13.541
Just prepare the following:

00:21:14.499 --> 00:21:16.000
One half cup of quinoa.

00:21:18.499 --> 00:21:20.499
One cup of water.

00:21:21.541 --> 00:21:22.958
One stalk of spring
onions, chopped.

00:21:23.958 --> 00:21:27.083
One red pepper, sliced thinly.

00:21:27.499 --> 00:21:29.708
One fourth cucumber, sliced.

00:21:29.875 --> 00:21:32.167
One half cup of orange juice.

00:21:32.499 --> 00:21:34.750
One teaspoon of lime juice.

00:21:35.625 --> 00:21:37.500
One tablespoon of balsamic syrup

00:21:38.083 --> 00:21:40.499
and a pinch of salt.

00:21:40.708 --> 00:21:42.499
To prepare, cook the
quinoa with water in a pot

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:46.625
for 15 minutes.

00:21:46.791 --> 00:21:47.875
Then let it cool.

00:21:51.499 --> 00:21:52.917
Mix all the vegetables together

00:21:54.499 --> 00:21:56.042
and combine it with
the cooked quinoa.

00:21:56.209 --> 00:21:58.499
For the dressing,

00:21:59.875 --> 00:22:01.000
just mix the orange
juice, lime juice,

00:22:01.375 --> 00:22:04.917
and balsamic syrup

00:22:05.083 --> 00:22:06.499
and drizzle it over
your mixed quinoa

00:22:09.125 --> 00:22:10.917
and vegetables.

00:22:11.083 --> 00:22:12.334
Add salt and pepper to taste.

